text: One of the Best Metro, well maintained, in East west corridor( EW= EW3.
A small estate, but full amenities. Supermarket,  shops and cooked food outlet available here.

The lift at Simei MRT really needs to improve its ventilation. It smells really terrible and as I’m agonised every time I need to take it!

I’m speaking as a Simei resident and mother who regularly use the lift for my baby’s stroller, and also, on behalf of other mothers and old folks.
Good place to visit there are few shopping have enjoyed

The malay guy there was very impatient and inconsiderate when my grandpa had a problem with his card. We were polite but he was basically just shouting commands at us, very impatient and rude because my grandpa couldnt understand english that well. Anyways i like the clinic there in the mrt.
